# Persona board (Norse)

Routing source: `.agents/workflows/sdd-persona-route.md`  
Detailed doc: `docs/09-subagent-personas.md` (Specialist persona board)

## When to run

Use a persona board when architecture, security, UX/content, release go/no-go, or risk acceptance needs **independent viewpoints** before progressing. `/sdd-loop` and `/sdd-verify` workflows may escalate here on conflict or critical uncertainty.

## Commands

- `/sdd-persona-board --preset <arch|security|ux|release|risk|bootstrap|spec|tasks>` (aliases normalize to canonical decision types)
- `/sdd-persona-list`, `/sdd-persona-route`, `/sdd-persona-report`, `/sdd-persona-resolve`, `/sdd-persona-health`
- `/sdd-board` is a **compatibility alias** for the Norse board flow

