## Durable outputs

Writes should land under:

- Reports: `.skillgrid/tasks/research/<change-id>/`
- Decision + state: `.skillgrid/tasks/context_<change-id>.md`
- Timeline: `.skillgrid/tasks/events/<change-id>.jsonl`

Board command returns must include contract fields: `personas_invoked`, `conflicts`, `hitl_required`, `accepted_decision` (plus standard `status`, `executive_summary`, `artifacts`, `next_recommended`, `risks`).
